race.description: Magic Millions March Yearling Sale Handicap (Bm70)
race.comment: HELL TO PAY (2) just ran into one better over this track and trip last time out and gets some weight relief with the 2kg claim. Looms as the main danger. READY FOR THE TRIP (3) loves it here on his home circuit with three wins and two placings from just five attempts. Will be hitting the line with gusto. The well-related INFLUENTIAL (1) (half to G3 winner Idle Flyer) has gotten better with each run this time in work and can trouble the judge with the right run from the inside alley. DELRICO (7) is resuming from a spell. Fitter for a recent trial at Sunshine Coast Inner Track. Opened last campaign with an eighth at Randwick Kensington over 1400m. Can go well.
